Draft compute-grant checkpoint log pointer
========================================

This records folder is intentionally a draft / non-record checkpoint.  It does
not include the full 8xH100 capture logs or bulky generated JSON result files.
Those artifacts are expected to live outside this PR folder, under the local
capture directory used in the README examples:

  artifacts/vast_8xh100_pr1493_capture_20260425_r3

Reference metrics from the final EMA checkpoint used for the pruning experiments:

  val_bpb  = 1.09238693
  val_loss = 2.82174889
  world_size = 8
  dataset = fineweb10B_sp8192
  tokenizer = fineweb_8192_bpe.model

This file exists so the draft non-record folder has an explicit log/status
pointer matching the README.  Full final logs should be regenerated and included
once the approach becomes a final submission candidate.
